<h2 id="actions-switch-language">ACTIONS - SWITCH LANGUAGE</h2>

<blockquote>
<p>ACTIONS - SWITCH LANGUAGE</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Changes the language Pepper is using. </p>

<aside type='info'>NOTE: Requires that you have a multilingual Dialogflow agent. Also note that this will change the language for the entire communication system involving Pepper.  This includes Pepper&rsquo;s language, the transcription service language, and the Dialogflow agent.  </aside>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight dialogflow tab-dialogflow"><code><span class="s2">"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
Dialogflow:  SWITCH THE LANGUAGE
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
I.) UI: 
By setting the 'style' payload, you can use the 'nextUtterance' feature to trigger a new intent. For a given intent within your agent, under the 'Response' section, select 'Custom Payload' and enter the following:
{
  "</span><span class="err">speak</span><span class="s2">": "</span><span class="err">Setting</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">background</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">image</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">and</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">color</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">||</span><span class="s2">",
  "</span><span class="err">action</span><span class="s2">": "</span><span class="err">setStyle</span><span class="s2">",
  "</span><span class="err">action_parameters</span><span class="s2">": {
    "</span><span class="err">backgroundColor</span><span class="s2">": "</span><span class="err">#ebc</span><span class="mi">6</span><span class="err">eb</span><span class="s2">",
    "</span><span class="err">backgroundImage</span><span class="s2">": "</span><span class="err">https</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="err">//pepperstoragedev.blob.core.windows.net/pepperdrive/</span><span class="mi">41092</span><span class="err">db</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="err">-ee</span><span class="mi">34-424</span><span class="err">a-bdf</span><span class="mi">3-6</span><span class="err">bca</span><span class="mi">579180</span><span class="err">afbd</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="err">dcbc</span><span class="mi">8</span><span class="err">-f</span><span class="mi">435-4615</span><span class="err">-b</span><span class="mi">63</span><span class="err">c</span><span class="mi">-4274</span><span class="err">d</span><span class="mi">66</span><span class="err">d</span><span class="mi">7993</span><span class="err">.png</span><span class="s2">",
    "</span><span class="err">restoreDefault</span><span class="s2">": false,
    "</span><span class="err">nextUtterance</span><span class="s2">": "</span><span class="err">Start</span><span class="s2">"
  }
}

</span></code></pre></div>
<p><img src = "images/Pepper_Data_Model-Play_A_Game.png"/></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight ms_bot_framework tab-ms_bot_framework"><code><span class="s2">"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
